I transcribed them.

00:29:19.424 --> 00:29:23.128 align:middle line:84%
Fred and I lost contact and
regained contact over the years

00:29:23.128 --> 00:29:24.763 align:middle line:90%
off and on.

00:29:24.763 --> 00:29:29.601 align:middle line:84%
And we finally decided to
put it together into a book,

00:29:29.601 --> 00:29:31.536 align:middle line:84%
and Hay House is planning
on releasing the book

00:29:31.536 --> 00:29:32.771 align:middle line:90%
