00:29:32.771 --> 00:29:35.607 align:middle line:84%
Oh, it's still to be-- the
story is still to be put out.

00:29:35.607 --> 00:29:36.274 align:middle line:90%
Fascinating.

00:29:36.274 --> 00:29:37.943 align:middle line:84%
Well, that actually
