00:31:19.978 --> 00:31:22.147 align:middle line:90%
How did you learn what it does?

00:31:22.147 --> 00:31:25.117 align:middle line:90%
How did you hone the skills?

00:31:25.117 --> 00:31:26.451 align:middle line:90%
And what did the lady say?

00:31:26.451 --> 00:31:28.453 align:middle line:90%
I forgot about that.

00:31:28.453 --> 00:31:29.755 align:middle line:90%
What did the lady say?

00:31:29.755 --> 00:31:32.557 align:middle line:84%
The psychic, when
you said that that--

00:31:32.557 --> 00:31:34.025 align:middle line:90%
I would call her periodically.

00:31:34.025 --> 00:31:39.297 align:middle line:84%
And I would say, twice a week,
the lamps are turning on.

00:31:39.297 --> 00:31:42.467 align:middle line:84%
And there's a door
somewhere in my home

00:31:42.467 --> 00:31:44.302 align:middle line:84%
that I've closed--
never the same door,

00:31:44.302 --> 00:31:45.937 align:middle line:90%
but I always close these doors.

00:31:45.937 --> 00:31:47.639 align:middle line:84%
And another door would
open, and it happens

00:31:47.639 --> 00:31:48.774 align:middle line:90%
in other people's houses.

00:31:48.774 --> 00:31:51.343 align:middle line:84%
And I explained the
blistering and the bleeding.

00:31:51.343 --> 00:31:55.814 align:middle line:84%
And her new age
platitudes would get

00:31:55.814 --> 00:31:57.749 align:middle line:90%
further and further stretched.

00:31:57.749 --> 00:32:00.218 align:middle line:84%
She was having
trouble responding.

00:32:00.218 --> 00:32:03.522 align:middle line:10%
By the time I told her about
the blistering and the bleeding

00:32:03.522 --> 00:32:05.757 align:middle line:10%
and the voices coming
through, she went,

00:32:05.757 --> 00:32:07.659 align:middle line:10%
I don't know what
to say about that.

00:32:07.659 --> 00:32:11.930 align:middle line:10%
Let me introduce you to the
woman who taught me this work.

00:32:11.930 --> 00:32:13.565 align:middle line:10%
And we can explain it there.

00:32:13.565 --> 00:32:16.668 align:middle line:10%
So I had a conversation with
her and with the other woman

00:32:16.668 --> 00:32:17.769 align:middle line:10%
and some other things.

00:32:17.769 --> 00:32:23.642 align:middle line:84%
And eventually, what it
pretty much came down to is

00:32:23.642 --> 00:32:26.144 align:middle line:84%
that you could say that
the woman who originated

00:32:26.144 --> 00:32:32.017 align:middle line:84%
the work that this woman on the
beach did for me created a key.

00:32:32.017 --> 00:32:34.252 align:middle line:84%
Let's just use an
analogy of a key.

00:32:34.252 --> 00:32:35.453 align:middle line:90%
She created a key.

00:32:35.453 --> 00:32:37.088 align:middle line:84%
Everyone she taught
how to do the work,

00:32:37.088 --> 00:32:38.657 align:middle line:84%
she taught them to do
it exactly the same,

00:32:38.657 --> 00:32:40.826 align:middle line:84%
so she gave them all
duplicates of this key.

00:32:40.826 --> 00:32:42.727 align:middle line:90%
She said, keep trying locks.

00:32:42.727 --> 00:32:43.762 align:middle line:90%
Keep trying doors.

00:32:43.762 --> 00:32:45.997 align:middle line:84%
Eventually this
will unlock a lock.

00:32:45.997 --> 00:32:48.967 align:middle line:90%
It'll open a door.

00:32:48.967 --> 00:32:50.669 align:middle line:90%
I was the door that the key fit.

00:32:50.669 --> 00:32:53.738 align:middle line:84%
It seems that nobody
had had this response

00:32:53.738 --> 00:32:56.308 align:middle line:84%
before or after me.
It was just me.

00:32:56.308 --> 00:32:58.009 align:middle line:84%
I was the door
that this key fit.

00:32:58.009 --> 00:33:01.279 align:middle line:84%
I'm not the gift, and we
need to bear that in mind.

00:33:01.279 --> 00:33:02.614 align:middle line:90%
I'm the door.

00:33:02.614 --> 00:33:04.983 align:middle line:84%
If Oprah Winfrey walks
in this door right here,

00:33:04.983 --> 00:33:06.585 align:middle line:84%
no one's going to run
over to the door and go,

00:33:06.585 --> 00:33:09.020 align:middle line:90%
wow, what a great door.

00:33:09.020 --> 00:33:09.721 align:middle line:90%
It's the gift.

00:33:09.721 --> 00:33:12.591 align:middle line:84%
As a matter of fact, the
woman who did this work to me

00:33:12.591 --> 00:33:14.893 align:middle line:84%
came back to me to
receive the gift.

00:33:14.893 --> 00:33:18.997 align:middle line:84%
In other words, she had the
key that unlocked the door

00:33:18.997 --> 00:33:20.899 align:middle line:90%
through which the gift came.

00:33:20.899 --> 00:33:23.001 align:middle line:84%
But she came to
receive the gift.

00:33:23.001 --> 00:33:25.070 align:middle line:84%
So would you say
that this key unlocks

00:33:25.070 --> 00:33:28.607 align:middle line:84%
various dimensions of energy,
of portals, would you say?

00:33:28.607 --> 00:33:29.574 align:middle line:90%
Absolutely.

00:33:29.574 --> 00:33:30.876 align:middle line:90%
Absolutely.

00:33:30.876 --> 00:33:36.748 align:middle line:84%
It takes us from a
four-dimensional existence

00:33:36.748 --> 00:33:38.516 align:middle line:84%
into a multi-dimensional
existence.

00:33:38.516 --> 00:33:42.420 align:middle line:84%
Now, some people
would like to think

00:33:42.420 --> 00:33:44.289 align:middle line:84%
of the multi-dimensional
existence

00:33:44.289 --> 00:33:47.659 align:middle line:84%
as the next level of
existence, next meaning

00:33:47.659 --> 00:33:49.294 align:middle line:90%
going from four to five.

00:33:49.294 --> 00:33:52.731 align:middle line:84%
But it's really a misnomer
to call it fifth dimensional,

00:33:52.731 --> 00:33:55.166 align:middle line:84%
because once you step
beyond four dimensions,

00:33:55.166 --> 00:33:58.470 align:middle line:84%
you're no longer linear,
so it cannot be five.

00:33:58.470 --> 00:34:02.073 align:middle line:84%
Once you hear someone talking
about sixth-dimensional or

00:34:02.073 --> 00:34:04.209 align:middle line:84%
26th-dimensional healing
or something like that,

00:34:04.209 --> 00:34:05.677 align:middle line:84%
the one thing you
can be assured of

00:34:05.677 --> 00:34:08.346 align:middle line:84%
is that they have no idea
what they're talking about.

00:34:08.346 --> 00:34:11.882 align:middle line:84%
Because once you step
into this space--

00:34:11.882 --> 00:34:12.784 align:middle line:90%
Time and space disappears.

00:34:12.784 --> 00:34:14.052 align:middle line:90%
Time is simultaneous.

00:34:14.052 --> 00:34:16.454 align:middle line:90%
Right, it disappears.

00:34:16.454 --> 00:34:20.525 align:middle line:84%
So if you're looking at this
from a limited four-dimensional

00:34:20.525 --> 00:34:22.360 align:middle line:84%
existence, then your
natural question

00:34:22.360 --> 00:34:24.429 align:middle line:84%
is, oh, I wonder
what might come next

00:34:24.429 --> 00:34:26.531 align:middle line:90%
after Reconnective Healing.

00:34:26.531 --> 00:34:29.434 align:middle line:84%
But if you step into the
multi-dimensional comprehension

00:34:29.434 --> 00:34:32.804 align:middle line:84%
of this, you realize that
that question is sort

00:34:32.804 --> 00:34:34.438 align:middle line:90%
of inappropriate or inaccurate.

00:34:34.438 --> 00:34:36.174 align:middle line:84%
There isn't something
that comes next.

00:34:36.174 --> 00:34:37.641 align:middle line:84%
-It's endless.
-Its endless.

00:34:37.641 --> 00:34:40.078 align:middle line:84%
Everything becomes
a simultaneous,

00:34:40.078 --> 00:34:42.781 align:middle line:90%
continuous expansion.

00:34:42.781 --> 00:34:48.219 align:middle line:84%
And it's teaching us how to
expand who and what we are.

00:34:48.219 --> 00:34:50.288 align:middle line:84%
So I can understand
that you would go on

00:34:50.288 --> 00:34:53.725 align:middle line:84%
to continue to heal
people and have them

00:34:53.725 --> 00:34:55.260 align:middle line:90%
have incredible experiences.

00:34:55.260 --> 00:34:58.763 align:middle line:84%
But sometimes the Western
mind needs to scientifically

00:34:58.763 --> 00:35:00.598 align:middle line:90%
validate what's happening here.

00:35:00.598 --> 00:35:02.167 align:middle line:90%
And that has been done on you.

00:35:02.167 --> 00:35:04.502 align:middle line:84%
And I appreciate the fact
that it has been done on you,

00:35:04.502 --> 00:35:07.939 align:middle line:84%
because it helps people
understand or maybe

00:35:07.939 --> 00:35:09.641 align:middle line:84%
look at this from a
linear perspective,

00:35:09.641 --> 00:35:11.176 align:middle line:90%
because that's what we do.

00:35:11.176 --> 00:35:15.313 align:middle line:84%
And although we know and
experience and feel and heel,

00:35:15.313 --> 00:35:18.917 align:middle line:84%
the linear mind sometimes wants
to grasp what this healing is.

00:35:18.917 --> 00:35:22.988 align:middle line:84%
And I am wide open,
and always have been,

00:35:22.988 --> 00:35:26.858 align:middle line:84%
to any legitimate
researchers who

00:35:26.858 --> 00:35:29.894 align:middle line:90%
want to do study on this work.

00:35:29.894 --> 00:35:30.962 align:middle line:90%
And there has been.

00:35:30.962 --> 00:35:33.431 align:middle line:84%
And there has been a lot
from around the world.

00:35:33.431 --> 00:35:36.001 align:middle line:84%
Now, the one thing
I'll say to you

00:35:36.001 --> 00:35:38.470 align:middle line:84%
is the one thing I say
to anyone, including

00:35:38.470 --> 00:35:40.739 align:middle line:84%
the researchers who don't
really like me saying this,

00:35:40.739 --> 00:35:47.779 align:middle line:84%
but I can't help it, because
this is my reality on this.

