00:53:18.262 --> 00:53:19.596 align:middle line:90%
and the swallowing increases.

00:53:22.199 --> 00:53:25.169 align:middle line:84%
This tends to happen
with virtually everyone

00:53:25.169 --> 00:53:27.571 align:middle line:90%
who's there at the seminars.

00:53:27.571 --> 00:53:29.873 align:middle line:90%
LISA GARR: Right.

00:53:29.873 --> 00:53:32.309 align:middle line:84%
And then when people
