00:53:34.945 --> 00:53:36.647 align:middle line:90%
Is that commonly what you hear?

00:53:36.647 --> 00:53:37.347 align:middle line:90%
ERIC PEARL: Yeah.

00:53:37.347 --> 00:53:40.484 align:middle line:84%
Now, remember, the seminars are
