00:53:41.618 --> 00:53:44.154 align:middle line:84%
The head tends to
rock and respond.

00:53:44.154 --> 00:53:45.355 align:middle line:90%
And the eyes move.

00:53:45.355 --> 00:53:48.525 align:middle line:84%
Remember, people are not
coming to the seminars

00:53:48.525 --> 00:53:50.160 align:middle line:90%
