00:53:50.160 --> 00:53:52.930 align:middle line:84%
They're coming to the seminars
to learn how to do the healing.

00:53:52.930 --> 00:53:54.832 align:middle line:84%
It's like if you're
going to medical school,

00:53:54.832 --> 00:53:56.867 align:middle line:84%
you're not going
to medical school

00:53:56.867 --> 00:53:58.602 align:middle line:84%
and confusing it with
a visit to your doctor.

00:53:58.602 --> 00:54:00.304 align:middle line:84%
You're going to
medical school to learn

00:54:00.304 --> 00:54:02.272 align:middle line:90%
how to become a doctor.

00:54:02.272 --> 00:54:05.008 align:middle line:90%
So that's part of what happens.

00:54:05.008 --> 00:54:07.277 align:middle line:84%
What occurs at the
seminars is it's

00:54:07.277 --> 00:54:09.947 align:middle line:84%
