all day Saturday, and all day

00:54:09.947 --> 00:54:10.848 align:middle line:90%
Sunday.

00:54:10.848 --> 00:54:12.950 align:middle line:84%
Friday night is a
three-hour presentation.

00:54:12.950 --> 00:54:15.152 align:middle line:84%
We talk about the
history of the work.

00:54:15.152 --> 00:54:18.789 align:middle line:84%
See the involuntary movement
of the fingers and the hands?

00:54:18.789 --> 00:54:20.491 align:middle line:84%
OK, those are some of
