00:54:32.035 --> 00:54:34.972 align:middle line:84%
And the people who
are working on them

00:54:34.972 --> 00:54:38.075 align:middle line:84%
are seminar attendees,
who've learned how to do it.

00:54:38.075 --> 00:54:39.977 align:middle line:84%
So again, I'll explain
how that works.

00:54:39.977 --> 00:54:43.180 align:middle line:84%
On a Friday night, generally I
give a three-hour presentation.

00:54:43.180 --> 00:54:45.315 align:middle line:84%
We talk about the history
of the work, the theory

00:54:45.315 --> 00:54:46.950 align:middle line:90%
of the work, the philosophy.

00:54:46.950 --> 00:54:48.919 align:middle line:84%
We bring up some
volunteers in the audience,

00:54:48.919 --> 00:54:50.821 align:middle line:84%
give live demonstrations
of the healing,

00:54:50.821 --> 00:54:52.789 align:middle line:84%
so you can see
the reality of it.

00:54:52.789 --> 00:54:54.758 align:middle line:84%
And we give everyone
an opportunity

00:54:54.758 --> 00:54:58.061 align:middle line:84%
to feel this in your hand, sort
of like I just did with you.

00:54:58.061 --> 00:55:00.130 align:middle line:84%
Saturday and Sunday is
very different, though.

00:55:00.130 --> 00:55:02.799 align:middle line:84%
It's a real, real
working seminar.

00:55:02.799 --> 00:55:05.235 align:middle line:84%
So I tell everyone-- and
I mean it-- don't come.

00:55:05.235 --> 00:55:07.437 align:middle line:84%
And I mean it-- don't come
if you think we're all going

00:55:07.437 --> 00:55:10.908 align:middle line:84%
to sit around and hold hands and
ohm and sing, kumbaya, my lord.

00:55:10.908 --> 00:55:12.876 align:middle line:90%
It won't happen that way.

00:55:12.876 --> 00:55:15.812 align:middle line:84%
We demonstrate a level of the
healing clearly from the stage,

00:55:15.812 --> 00:55:19.383 align:middle line:84%
then we all go to massage
tables in groups of two or four,

00:55:19.383 --> 00:55:20.083 align:middle line:90%
give or take.

00:55:20.083 --> 00:55:22.452 align:middle line:84%
I walk around to each
of the tables myself.

00:55:22.452 --> 00:55:24.254 align:middle line:84%
So does our team of
teaching assistants.

00:55:24.254 --> 00:55:27.424 align:middle line:84%
We help teach you how to
feel this, how to find it.

00:55:27.424 --> 00:55:29.526 align:middle line:84%
You start to see the
person on the table

00:55:29.526 --> 00:55:31.828 align:middle line:84%
go into involuntary
physical registers,

00:55:31.828 --> 00:55:33.530 align:middle line:90%
like we just saw on the tape.

00:55:33.530 --> 00:55:35.465 align:middle line:84%
Then we teach you how
to feel something else,

00:55:35.465 --> 00:55:37.801 align:middle line:84%
and you see their registers
change to something else,

00:55:37.801 --> 00:55:42.239 align:middle line:84%
and you begin to recognize
your clear distinct interaction

00:55:42.239 --> 00:55:44.074 align:middle line:84%
with escorting them
into a healing place.

00:55:44.074 --> 00:55:47.611 align:middle line:84%
And by the end of that one
weekend-- one weekend, not six

00:55:47.611 --> 00:55:50.914 align:middle line:84%
months or a year, one
weekend-- I can pretty much

00:55:50.914 --> 00:55:52.616 align:middle line:90%
make you two promises.

00:55:52.616 --> 00:55:54.985 align:middle line:84%
A, you will be
able to do anything

00:55:54.985 --> 00:55:57.287 align:middle line:84%
and everything in the way
of healing that I can do.

00:55:57.287 --> 00:56:00.257 align:middle line:84%
And B, you will be able to
do anything and everything

00:56:00.257 --> 00:56:03.260 align:middle line:84%
in the way of healing that
any human being anywhere

00:56:03.260 --> 00:56:05.362 align:middle line:84%
on this planet can do, whether
they were raised by monks

00:56:05.362 --> 00:56:07.931 align:middle line:84%
in a cave and a mountaintop in
Tibet and fed grains of seed,

00:56:07.931 --> 00:56:10.867 align:middle line:84%
each one blessed by its
own individual Lama.

00:56:10.867 --> 00:56:12.736 align:middle line:90%
It doesn't matter the story.

00:56:12.736 --> 00:56:15.339 align:middle line:84%
You know what matters
today is our willingness

00:56:15.339 --> 00:56:17.341 align:middle line:90%
to transcend the story.

00:56:17.341 --> 00:56:23.880 align:middle line:84%
We are given a gift of
being able to demystify

00:56:23.880 --> 00:56:25.816 align:middle line:90%
the healing process.

00:56:25.816 --> 00:56:27.918 align:middle line:84%
The challenge is whether or
not we're willing to allow

00:56:27.918 --> 00:56:29.319 align:middle line:90%
it to be demystified.

00:56:29.319 --> 00:56:33.090 align:middle line:84%
We're given a gift today of
transcending the complications,

00:56:33.090 --> 00:56:36.960 align:middle line:84%
the fear-based rituals, and
control-based techniques

00:56:36.960 --> 00:56:37.861 align:middle line:90%
of healing.

00:56:37.861 --> 00:56:39.363 align:middle line:84%
And the challenge
is whether or not

00:56:39.363 --> 00:56:41.365 align:middle line:84%
we're willing to
transcend the techniques

00:56:41.365 --> 00:56:43.033 align:middle line:90%
to achieve greater healings.

00:56:43.033 --> 00:56:45.636 align:middle line:84%
And the question then
becomes, if we're not

00:56:45.636 --> 00:56:48.505 align:middle line:84%
willing to transcend the
techniques to access more,

00:56:48.505 --> 00:56:50.407 align:middle line:90%
we need to ask ourselves why.

00:56:50.407 --> 00:56:53.110 align:middle line:84%
If we're not willing to allow
the healing process to become

00:56:53.110 --> 00:56:56.346 align:middle line:84%
clearer and demystified,
transparent for everyone,

00:56:56.346 --> 00:56:57.781 align:middle line:90%
we need to ask ourselves why.

00:56:57.781 --> 00:56:59.816 align:middle line:84%
And if we're not willing
to ask ourselves why,

00:56:59.816 --> 00:57:03.053 align:middle line:84%
then we need to ask ourselves
why we're not willing to ask

00:57:03.053 --> 00:57:06.223 align:middle line:84%
ourselves why, because it's
within that question that

00:57:06.223 --> 00:57:09.293 align:middle line:90%
lies the gift to our mastery.

00:57:09.293 --> 00:57:11.928 align:middle line:84%
It's very, very
empowering, your message is.

00:57:11.928 --> 00:57:13.730 align:middle line:84%
And it takes the guru
out of the picture

00:57:13.730 --> 00:57:16.867 align:middle line:84%
and puts the healing into
our own responsibility.

00:57:16.867 --> 00:57:17.768 align:middle line:84%
-Our own hands.
-Yeah.

00:57:17.768 --> 00:57:19.336 align:middle line:90%
Our own hands, basically.

00:57:19.336 --> 00:57:21.204 align:middle line:90%
And so, thank you so much.

